## tunnels

Host irc-tunnel
     User mort
     HostName punk.recoil.org
     IdentityFile ~/.ssh/bitbucket-key
     LocalForward 7000 chat.freenode.net:7000

Host opw-tunnel
     User mort
     HostName punk.recoil.org
     IdentityFile ~/.ssh/bitbucket-key
     LocalForward 7070 irc.gnome.org:7000

